{
  "stem": "24466.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in the Russian-- in the-- they-- they have to be, you know, a place through the forest, you know, to go-- where the boots are sinking in the--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Swamps, swamps.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lewin, but I don't know his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Happens that everything was packed, the whole town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a Jewish little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the town where the first president, Chaim Weizmann was born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Motala.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "M-O-T-A-L-A, not far from Pinsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they packed everything, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some horses and what they call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Carts, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were back, and that was one of-- that-- that wasn't not far from the station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a special one, wagon-- wagon, yes?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was prepared for, them and everything was packed in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were with the-- on the-- the train, we went to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next day the annexations happened, that Lithuania took over Vilna, and the whole part of [NON-ENGLISH], they called us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came to Vilna, I remember [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my father mentioned to me once a name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lichtenstein.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was practicing under him, that he is occupying a very high post in a tannery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Salman's tannery.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-A-L-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember that he told me this, because when I finished gymnasium, my father and I was trying to get to start an engineering something to do.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father told me, listen, it would be a good thing if you will go, because practically I can see you are very gifted in tanning, and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would be of interest that you would do-- you will become a master tanner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he mentioned that name Lichtenstein.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
